| Product | Price | Quantity |
| ------- | ----- | -------- |
| Rice    | 50    | 2        |
| Milk    | 30    | 3        |
| Bread   | 40    | 1        |
| Eggs    | 6     | 12       |
| Sugar   | 45    | 2        |
